    <div class="faq-a" id="how-do-i-find-keywords-for-a-service-area-business"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Service-area businesses face a unique challenge. They cannot rank in the local pack for cities where they have no physical location. Focus on organic rankings with city-specific landing pages. Target "service + city" keywords with dedicated pages for each major service area. Build local citations in each target city. And consider a virtual office or co-working space in your highest-value market to establish a physical presence.</p></div></div>
