    <div class="faq-a" id="how-long-does-it-take-to-rank-for-local-keywords"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>New websites typically take 3-6 months to rank for local keywords. Established websites with strong GBP profiles can see results in 4-8 weeks. The timeline depends on competition, your current authority, and how consistently you implement local SEO tactics. Map pack rankings often improve faster than organic rankings because proximity is a major ranking factor.</p></div></div>
